{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people weren't waiting in the line, weren't waiting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They started to climb the fence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And while it was-- at that time I thought, this is worst thing that could happen, that I am stuck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I will be  in Sobibor, because the moment I went through this hole, at that point, the fence, under the heaviness of the bodies, of the people climbing, collapsed and pinned me down.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I realized that this was my luck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, while lying under the fence, people stepping over me, I've seen bodies taken apart by the mines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And later, when everybody went through, I did try to climb out and wasn't able, because the barbs had embedded in my coat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And luckily, I had a leather coat, because I picked it up from the storerooms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And  it didn't go too deep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I just slid out from this leather coat and left the coat on the barbed-wires.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was probably the last one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I  did fall down a couple times, I remember, in the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I thought I'm hit .",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I did get up and run until I reached the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I reached the forest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how long I did run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But at that point, I did come to a group of people, and I stopped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was our assembling point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sasha was with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he counted us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were about 50 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he instructed us to not to smoke cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I remember, I've seen Kali Mali later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we met another group of prisoners, later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were afraid that this was a German setup, because, from far away, we've seen a group of people coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we laid down.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
